Class ECUtil

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.jcajce.provider.asymmetric.util.ECUtil
public class ECUtil extends Object
utility class for converting jce/jca ECDSA, ECDH, and ECDHC objects into their com.distrimind.bouncycastle.crypto counterparts.
